sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:193:| PAL-004 | Load saved PAL action plans by run id. | MUST | T1 | Test loads `outputs/action-results.json` from a fixture run. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:194:| PAL-005 | Reject approvals for actions absent from the saved plan. | MUST | T1 | CLI returns nonzero and writes no execution artifact. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:195:| PAL-006 | Reject approvals for unknown action ids. | MUST | T1 | Test proves unknown ids never reach the action runner. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:196:| PAL-007 | Execute an approved saved action without a model call. | MUST | T1 | Fake PAL client records zero `query()` calls during replay. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:197:| PAL-008 | Write approval execution artifacts. | MUST | T1 | Artifact contains action id, status, timestamp, and redacted command output. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:198:| PAL-009 | Link approval execution artifacts to the source plan. | MUST | T1 | Artifact stores source run id and source action-plan path. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:199:| PAL-010 | Harden `restart_router` for host-managed PAL. | MUST | T1 | Unit test verifies `/opt/pal/scripts/start_router.sh` is preferred. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:200:| PAL-011 | Keep Docker restart as fallback only. | MUST | T1 | Unit test verifies Docker is selected only when host script is absent. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:201:| PAL-012 | Add fake SSH runner support for PAL tests. | MUST | T1 | Tests run remote-action code without a real SSH connection. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:202:| PAL-013 | Create PAL source discovery function. | MUST | T2 | Test returns configured sample files. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:203:| PAL-014 | Add deterministic PAL knowledge chunking. | MUST | T2 | Test proves stable chunk ids for unchanged input files. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:204:| PAL-015 | Add PAL knowledge index writer. | MUST | T2 | `pal kb build` creates `.promptclaw/pal-kb/index.jsonl` or SQLite equivalent. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:205:| PAL-016 | Add PAL knowledge query command. | MUST | T2 | Query returns ranked snippets with source paths. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:206:| PAL-017 | Inject PAL knowledge into workflow prompts. | MUST | T2 | Prompt artifact includes a bounded `Knowledge Context` section. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:207:| PAL-018 | Add slow-inference context collection. | MUST | T2 | Workflow captures health, baseline token/s, GPU hints, and logs when available. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:208:| PAL-019 | Add slow-inference diagnosis CLI. | MUST | T2 | Command writes a diagnosis run artifact and performs no mutation. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:209:| PAL-020 | Add restart-validation workflow. | MUST | T2 | Command runs health, direct query, smoke, Tailscale, and process checks. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:210:| PAL-021 | Add shutdown-audit workflow. | MUST | T2 | Summary states shutdown enabled state, override state, and next shutdown window. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:211:| PAL-022 | Add Phase 2 readiness workflow. | MUST | T2 | Report scores each prerequisite and exposes no Phase 2 execution action. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:212:| PAL-023 | Standardize PAL workflow `run-summary.json`. | MUST | T1 | Every workflow writes required workflow/status/tool/action keys. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:213:| PAL-024 | Add PAL workflow artifact verifier. | MUST | T1 | Test fails a run missing required artifacts. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:214:| PAL-025 | Add PAL secret redaction verifier. | MUST | T1 | Test fails artifacts containing `PAL_SSH_KEY` or token-like values. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:215:| PAL-026 | Add PAL escalation artifact helper. | MUST | T1 | Missing SSH env and pending approval write `summary/escalation.md`. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:216:| PAL-027 | Create repo-managed PAL deployment manifest. | MUST | T2 | Manifest lists intended `/opt/pal` files and contains no secrets. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:217:| PAL-028 | Implement deploy diff model. | MUST | T2 | Fake remote test reports diff sets. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:218:| PAL-029 | Implement deploy-plan CLI. | MUST | T2 | Command prints plan with no remote writes. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:219:| PAL-030 | Implement deploy backup primitive. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test stores changed files. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:220:| PAL-031 | Implement approved deploy-apply CLI. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test requires approval flag. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:221:| PAL-032 | Implement rollback primitive. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test restores backed-up files. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:222:| PAL-033 | Add `promptclaw pal deploy rollback --approve-rollback`. | SHOULD | T2 | Command refuses rollback without approval flag. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:223:| PAL-034 | Add PAL deployment metadata model. | SHOULD | T1 | Metadata stores hourly rate, runtime estimate, and optional Vast instance id. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:224:| PAL-035 | Add `promptclaw pal cost`. | SHOULD | T1 | Command prints hourly, daily, and monthly burn estimates. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:225:| PAL-036 | Add Vast connector stub boundary. | MUST | T2 | No rent/destroy/start/stop action is callable by default. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:226:| PAL-037 | Add Vast secret redaction tests. | MUST | T1 | Tests reject persisted Vast API key values. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:227:| PAL-038 | Update architecture documentation. | MUST | T1 | Docs include a PAL platform section. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:228:| PAL-039 | Update command reference documentation. | MUST | T1 | Docs list all new `promptclaw pal` commands. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:229:| PAL-040 | Update PAL project guide. | MUST | T1 | `pal-2026/docs/PROJECT_GUIDE.md` names the new operator loop. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:230:| PAL-041 | Add fake-client CLI tests for PAL workflows. | MUST | T2 | Tests cover kb, approve, workflow, and deploy-plan commands. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:231:| PAL-042 | Add opt-in live PAL verification marker or script. | MUST | T1 | Default test run skips live checks. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:232:| PAL-043 | Document live PAL verification commands. | MUST | T1 | Handoff lists health, smoke, triage, proposal-only, and read-only action checks. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:233:| PAL-044 | Create SDP handoff page. | MUST | T1 | Page lists analyze and run-loop commands. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:234:| PAL-045 | Update changelog for PAL agentic ops. | MUST | T1 | Changelog entry names approval replay, KB, workflows, and deploy plan. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:242:1. Approval replay and action metadata hardening: PAL-002 through PAL-012.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:243:2. Knowledge base: PAL-013 through PAL-017.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:244:3. Workflow family: PAL-018 through PAL-026.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:245:4. Deployment tooling: PAL-027 through PAL-033.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:246:5. Cost/Vast boundary: PAL-034 through PAL-037.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:247:6. Docs, tests, live verification, and SDP handoff: PAL-038 through PAL-045.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:249:Do not start deployment apply or rollback before the dry-run deployment plan and fake-remote tests are green.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:286:Required live checks before marking the PRD deployable:
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:296:Mutating live checks such as `restart_router`, `pause_shutdown_once`, `resume_shutdown`, deploy apply, rollback, or any Vast API action must not run unless Anthony explicitly approves that exact action.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:315:Deployment is a product deliverable, but deployment execution must be gated:
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:318:2. Create dry-run deploy plan.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:320:4. Require explicit `--approve-deploy`.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:321:5. Back up remote files.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:325:9. Write deployment artifact locally under `.promptclaw/pal-deploy/`.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:327:The deploy implementation must support the current host-managed PAL runtime. It may support Docker as an additional deployment mode, but Docker cannot be the only path.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:335:| SDP agents assume Docker because older guide used Docker | High | Medium | PAL-010 and PAL-011 require host-managed restart selection tests and Docker fallback-only behavior. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:336:| Approval replay accidentally re-plans with model and executes a different action | Medium | High | PAL-002 forbids model calls during replay; tests must assert fake client is not called. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:337:| Knowledge index grows with noisy run artifacts | Medium | Low | PAL-013 through PAL-015 bind source discovery, chunking, and index writing to deterministic tests. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:338:| Live deployment apply breaks the PAL router | Medium | High | PAL-029 through PAL-031 require deploy plan, backup primitive, and explicit apply approval. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:340:| PAL recommends Phase 2 too early | Medium | Medium | PAL-022 requires a report-only workflow with no Phase 2 execution action. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:341:| Vast API connector causes spend or destructive actions | Low | High | PAL-036 and PAL-037 require stub-only Vast boundary and secret redaction tests. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:363:4. Whether deployment package files live under `pal-2026/deploy/` or `promptclaw/pal_deploy/` plus project templates.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:396:After implementation tasks finish, stage/deploy using the SDP deploy path:
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:400:sdp-cli deploy
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:403:Do not run mutating PAL deploy or cloud spend actions unless Anthony explicitly approves them after reading the generated dry-run plan.
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:409:- v1.0 - 2026-05-15 - Initial SDP PRD for end-to-end PAL 2026 agentic operations, knowledge base, workflow engine, approval replay, deployment tooling, and verification gates.
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:3:Four systems need work in the right order: **CypherClaw** (art organism), **PromptClaw** (toolkit/dev), **sdp-cli** (core pipeline), **R750** (work deployment). This document sequences all of them to avoid thrashing, blocked dependencies, or duplicated effort.
